name: stock_get_five_yr_avg_div_yield
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool yh_finance_v2.
Tool description: 
API description: Fetches the five-year average dividend yield for a given stock symbol and region.

symbol.description: Ticker Symbol ( Ex. \\\\\\\\\"AAPL\\\\\\\\\" is Ticker symbol for Apple Inc. on the stock market )

region.description: The region of the stock market. Allowed values are 'US', 'BR', 'AU', 'CA', 'FR', 'DE', 'HK', 'IN', 'IT', 'ES', 'GB', 'S'. Default is 'US'.
